author: mgrigorov
msg: WICKET-3700 WicketTester.startComponent(Class, Markup) doesn't deliver the contributed response to the headers
Don't use Markup.of() because it creates a MarkupResourceStream without ContainerInfo and thus no HtmlHeaderContainer is created.
Create manually MarkupResourceStream and pass it to MarkupParser.parse() instead.
The markup for the autogenerated page is extended with html, head and body tags so it really looks like a page markup.
